## How It Works

### Architecture

```
Input string
    │
    ▼
 Lexer  ──► Vec<Token>
    │
    ▼
 Parser (recursive descent)
    │
    ▼
  f64 result (or CalcError)
```

### Operator Precedence (low → high)

| Level | Operators | Associativity |
|-------|-----------|---------------|
| 1     | `+` `-`   | Left          |
| 2     | `*` `/` `%` | Left        |
| 3     | `^`       | **Right**     |
| 4     | Unary `-` `+` | Right     |
| 5     | `(` `)`, literals | —     |

